                        <placeName key="place_113989">Norton</placeName>, <placeName key="place_113991">'Rodanhangra' [lost]</placeName>, <placeName key="place_113990">Oxhey</placeName>. King Ethelred to St Albans Abbey; grant of land at Norton, 'Rodanhangra'
                        and Oxhey, Herts., originally granted to the abbey by King Offa but
                        subsequently lost, and later forfeited to King Ethelred by Ealdorman
                        Leofsige, and purchased for St Albans by Archbishop Aelfric and Abbot
                        Leofric. <origDate when="1007">1007</origDate>
                     </p>
